( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:18,940 --> 00:00:23,880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

2
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

3
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:37,010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

4
00:00:38,210 --> 00:00:43,120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

5
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:47,930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

6
00:00:47,930 --> 00:00:51,000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

7
00:00:51,710 --> 00:00:56,660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

8
00:00:57,700 --> 00:01:00,880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

9
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:04,160
♪The open sky rises high♪

10
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:09,830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

11
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:13,860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

12
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:17,220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

13
00:01:17,630 --> 00:01:23,300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

14
00:01:23,710 --> 00:01:26,960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

15
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:30,290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

16
00:01:30,690 --> 00:01:34,730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

17
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:35,980
=The Lead=

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 22=

19
00:01:37,980 --> 00:01:39,900
(Castration of pigs, cattle and
donkeys and veterinary care)

20
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,440
I thought breeding meant

21
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:48,000
taking animals to the breeding station.

22
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:50,000
But look at you.

23
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,640
Leading bulls and male donkeys around,

24
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,840
looking everywhere for females.

25
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,440
It's the busy farming season.

26
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,880
All the animals are working in the fields.

27
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,440
Who has time for the breeding station?

28
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,320
So we have to make house calls.

29
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,040
Good thing they are animals.

30
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,160
Sanyuan.

31
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:09,280
Tonight, try my cooking.

32
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,360
Braised pig testicles.

33
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,320
They'll be amazing.

34
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:12,480
You've never had anything like it.

35
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,720
What are you writing?

36
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,640
A drum score.

37
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,190
What drum score?

38
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,440
Yang Men Nyu Jiang.

39
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,720
The troupe dropped you.

40
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,960
And you still won't give up?

41
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:26,200
After years inside, I realized

42
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,800
the world outside had changed.

43
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:30,640
Back when I went in,

44
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,790
people just wanted enough to eat.

45
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,640
So much time has passed.

46
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,840
Now, everyone was shouting,

47
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:40,560
"Boost business and get rich."

48
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,600
Now, everywhere you look,

49
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,440
people are chasing money.

50
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,600
Stop clinging to those drumsticks.

51
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,080
Find a new way to live, fast.

52
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,360
You can breed donkeys,
do pig castration...

53
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,960
Besides the two drumsticks,

54
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,160
what else do I know?

55
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:57,600
Then go tap people's backs.

56
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,760
I can't live off that.

57
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,080
These are for fire breathing.

58
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,160
Starting today,

59
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,360
during the day, you do Yang Men Nyu Jiang.

60
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:16,200
At night, we four do Gui Yuan Sha Sheng.

61
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,440
No one else can watch.

62
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,040
But you must stay right by me.

63
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,800
Fire breathing is the
Dan role's secret skill.

64
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,440
You have to master it.

65
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,200
Remember,

66
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,480
never panic during fire breathing.

67
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,360
Once you hold this in your mouth,

68
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,000
sink your qi to the dantian.

69
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,200
Use abdominal breathing.

70
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,200
Keep your breath under control.

71
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,360
And the plosive sounds.

72
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,200
Watch.

73
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,600
Whatever you do, don't panic.

74
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:32,920
♪Dear son, you softly beg♪

75
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:39,080
♪To go to battle♪

76
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,240
♪If you have real skill♪

77
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,560
♪Mother won't worry♪

78
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:54,920
♪I ponder secretly in my heart♪

79
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:59,480
♪My mind is made up♪

80
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:10,520
♪Competing on the training ground♪

81
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:28,240
♪I hold back a bit for my son♪

82
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,640
Stop, stop.

83
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,680
What do you

84
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,760
think about your performance?

85
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,560
It was okay.

86
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,840
It was bad.

87
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,280
Why was it bad?

88
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,080
I don't know.

89
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:15,640
Are you seeing someone?

90
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:19,920
No.

91
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,520
Tell the truth.

92
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,280
I'm not.

93
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,680
Do you have a crush on someone?

94
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,720
No.

95
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,760
You don't like Feng Xiaoxiao?

96
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,040
Why do we call eyes "lamps"?

97
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,760
Through them, I can see into your heart.

98
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,240
What's in your heart

99
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:47,920
is plain

100
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,640
as day.

101
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,080
You can fool no one.

102
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,760
When you played the scene,

103
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,560
from the look alone

104
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,840
wasn't Mu Guiying and Yang Wenguang.

105
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,720
It was Mu Guiying and Yang Zongbao.

106
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,720
A mother-son bond

107
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:08,720
was turned into a loving couple by you two.

108
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,680
The eye training

109
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:18,560
was to clear stray thoughts

110
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,800
and keep your mind on the play alone.

111
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,520
But you

112
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,680
got even more stray thoughts.

113
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,680
You're still young.

114
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,360
You mustn't date.

115
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:33,680
I'm not dating anyone.

116
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,720
Stop arguing.

117
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,240
Before you become a star performer,

118
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,480
you must only care about acting.

119
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,480
Nothing else is allowed.

120
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,400
Do you hear me?

121
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,360
Answer me.

122
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,640
Know why?

123
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,680
They will hold you back.

124
00:09:31,260 --> 00:09:34,480
♪I came down from the mountains♪

125
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,600
♪Carrying orchid grass♪

126
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:41,460
♪I planted it in my little garden♪

127
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:44,000
♪Hoping it would bloom soon♪

128
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:47,720
♪I checked on it three times a day♪

129
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:50,530
♪Watching it as the days went by♪

130
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,760
♪Yet the orchid still♪

131
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:56,760
♪Had not a single bud♪

132
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,920
Looking for me?

133
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,720
Wait...

134
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,400
Why are you ignoring me?

135
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,360
What did I do wrong?

136
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,840
What did Chu Jiahe say to you?

137
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:48,880
Tell me.

138
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,120
Tell me, or I'll go ask her.

139
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,920
I... I'm going.

140
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,640
She didn't say anything.

141
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,200
I did.

142
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:00,360
What did you say?

143
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,680
I said I won't fight her for Mu Guiying.

144
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:04,080
But she can't steal you from me.

145
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,440
Yi Qing'e.

146
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,360
Yi Qing'e!

147
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,160
I also said

148
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:14,200
that you're already mine.

149
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,400
I won't give you up to her.

150
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,200
Since when am I yours?

151
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,520
Didn't we go roller skating together?

152
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,880
Didn't I sing while you played?

153
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:26,040
Didn't we watch movies together?

154
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,840
Didn't you eat my candy?

155
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:30,030
Or meat from my bowl?

156
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:31,000
Hey!

157
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,600
Being close isn't the same as dating!

158
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:36,080
What you think and I think differ.

159
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,800
If I say we're dating, we are.

160
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,240
Why are you so unreasonable?

161
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,200
My reasons are all that matter.

162
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,360
You don't have to be with me.

163
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,640
You can be with someone else.

164
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,280
But you can't be with her.

165
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,440
Why?

166
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,280
Who I choose is none of your business.

167
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,320
She wants rice,

168
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,880
and she wants Mo too.

169
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,810
All the good things

170
00:11:53,810 --> 00:11:55,680
can't all go to her alone.

171
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,280
A dog said that.

172
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,520
Dog?

173
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,440
Is that what I meant?

174
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,160
Did I mean it like that?

175
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,400
Was that my point?

176
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,600
Yi Qing'e.

177
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,040
Well, I did say that.

178
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,240
But that's not what I meant.

179
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,760
I meant those girls.

180
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:16,960
Yi Qing'e.

181
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,800
You should go.

182
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,840
Don't play here anymore.

183
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,440
What's wrong?

184
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,200
Did she scare you?

185
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,200
You were so bold as a kid.

186
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,320
Catching snakes, fighting Er Laizi.

187
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,680
Why have you grown more timid?

188
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:31,280
It has nothing to do with her.

189
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,360
"Nothing to do with her"?

190
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,400
There's someone else?

191
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,960
My master.

192
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,400
Which master?

193
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,480
Master Gou.

194
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,760
What did he tell you?

195
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:54,880
Tell me.

196
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:58,880
How about this?

197
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,040
If you tell me,

198
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,760
I'll never play here again.

199
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,280
He said my heart must hold only opera.

200
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:11,440
Nothing else is allowed in.

201
00:14:22,880 --> 00:14:26,000
♪Horses race, startled birds cry♪

202
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:29,560
♪Winding roads fade into empty hills♪

203
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:30,720
- ♪All the way♪
- Stop!

204
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,000
Yi Qing'e, Feng Xiaoxiao,

205
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,120
and Chu Jiahe!

206
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,320
What's going on with you?

207
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,000
Sleepy?

208
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:42,440
Everyone else is doing fine.

209
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,600
Except the three of you.

210
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,600
You're flat and totally lifeless.

211
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,440
What's on your mind?

212
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,440
Everyone else, take a break.

213
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,840
You three, stay right there

214
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,120
and get your focus back!

215
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,640
When you do, we'll continue.

216
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,490
If you can't,

217
00:14:53,490 --> 00:14:54,600
you'll keep standing there!

218
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,280
What's going on?

219
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:02,840
It was just one.

220
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,360
Now all three have issues.

221
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,440
How would I know?

222
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,160
I only taught Yi Qing'e.

223
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,840
I didn't teach the other two.

224
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,440
You taught her that?

225
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,800
What even was that?

226
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,920
Look at you.

227
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,600
Do you have to be so angry?

228
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:18,040
All right, all right.

229
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,480
Ignore that old coot.

230
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,640
What kind of mess is this?

231
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,480
Just look at them.

232
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:32,760
No spark inside, none in their eyes.

233
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,120
Hu Sanyuan?

234
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,320
Why are you back?

235
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,360
- What?
- Take it.

236
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:45,760
What is it?

237
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:48,560
The Yang Men Nyu Jiang drum score.

238
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:49,680
Give it a try.

239
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:50,520
What?

240
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:52,080
Teaching me the drums?

241
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:04,830
- Let's eat first.
- Okay.

242
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,320
Come with me.

243
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:29,360
You needed me, Master Gou?

244
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,440
There's a rule for trainees.

245
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,040
No dating allowed.

246
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:36,800
You know that, right?

247
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,120
I know.

248
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,840
How serious are you two?

249
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:44,720
Us two? Me and who?

250
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,360
Yi Qing'e.

251
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,520
We're not dating.

252
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,680
Chu Jiahe likes you, too, right?

253
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,800
You can't fool me.

254
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:58,600
I'm not fooling anyone.

255
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,760
I don't care if you date Chu Jiahe.

256
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,120
But not Yi Qing'e.

257
00:17:04,600 --> 00:17:05,640
I don't like Chu Jiahe.

258
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,120
You can't like Yi Qing'e either!

259
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,240
Why not?

260
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:11,520
In Yi Qing'e's heart,

261
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,840
there's no room for two things.

262
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:17,200
You can tell from her acting

263
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,640
these past few days.

264
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,920
Who says we can only act

265
00:17:21,320 --> 00:17:22,280
and can't date?

266
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,720
It's not that you can't.

267
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,880
Just not right now.

268
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,480
Her heart must stay with the play,

269
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,880
and with the role.

270
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:05,480
Plump.

271
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:06,520
Your bowl.

272
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:07,360
Yeah.

273
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:54,040
I never imagined that kid

274
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,240
would make it this far.

275
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:58,080
When I brought her out,

276
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:00,400
I just wanted her to have food,

277
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,160
and ease my sister's burden.

278
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:03,640
Who would've thought?

279
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,800
The kid owes you.

280
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:07,320
I owe you too.

281
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:09,720
I'll never forget it.

282
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:12,960
You've got that wrong.

283
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:15,160
You brought the kid out.

284
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,520
So even at my age,

285
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:18,080
I finally did something right.

286
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:22,440
Where's the old Hu Sanyuan?

287
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:25,760
You're still the same

288
00:19:25,760 --> 00:19:27,240
Master Gu I always looked

289
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,080
up to.

290
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,800
When I heard you came out early,

291
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:33,880
I wondered where to find you.

292
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,840
Director Gu, look.

293
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:37,040
Now he's back, no need to worry.

294
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:38,480
The past few days,

295
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:40,160
He Dachui's drum

296
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:42,320
had him too worried to sleep.

297
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:45,200
I've written the drum score.

298
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,800
I came here

299
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:48,160
to give He Dachui the drum score.

300
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,680
That won't help at all.

301
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:53,280
Even if you carve it on the drum,

302
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:56,200
he still won't play it right.

303
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,040
From now on,

304
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,880
you play the drum for us.

305
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,040
Yeah.

306
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:04,720
I need to head back soon.

307
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:05,640
I've got work to do.

308
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:07,280
What kind of work?

309
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,720
Pig castration.

310
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:11,560
What?

311
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:36,320
Mother, if you don't lose,

312
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:38,160
I won't be able to serve the country.

313
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:40,480
Please show mercy and let me go.

314
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,410
- Mother...
- Stop.

315
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,240
Yi Qing'e.

316
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,680
What's wrong with you?

317
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,400
We've rehearsed this

318
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,280
for days.

319
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:52,080
You're drifting further off.

320
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,240
Each take gets worse!

321
00:20:55,800 --> 00:20:57,160
Where are your eyes looking?

322
00:20:58,040 --> 00:20:59,240
Yang Wenguang is right there.

323
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,760
Why look at Yang Qiniang?

324
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:12,400
Kid, stay focused in rehearsal.

325
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,880
Don't let your eyes wander.

326
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:18,080
Mr. Dachui.

327
00:21:18,080 --> 00:21:18,920
What?

328
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:19,960
Could you

329
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:22,680
play it from this drum score?

330
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,520
Why?

331
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:24,960
No reason.

332
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,840
Just try it.

333
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,200
See how it feels.

334
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,600
What did you even draw here?

335
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:33,200
I can't read it.

336
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:34,480
I can't play this.

337
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,000
I just can't.

338
00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:37,880
I can't.

339
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:45,440
Rehearsal over!

340
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:50,400
Since Hu Sanyuan is back,

341
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:53,200
I want him on drums for this show.

342
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,360
He can't do it.

343
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,440
Just because he went to prison?

344
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:03,880
For this show, He Dachui has been

345
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,600
practicing really hard

346
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:06,880
to sharpen his skills.

347
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:07,720
I heard it.

348
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,120
He's not that far off.

349
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:10,720
What he lacks isn't skills.

350
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,720
It's not about his hands.

351
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:15,080
A man who can't accept one drum score

352
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:17,720
lacks vision and heart.

353
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:19,560
Let me make this clear.

354
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:22,080
Even if he drums himself into the ground,

355
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:23,400
he still can't play the spirit

356
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:25,400
of Yang Men Nyu Jiang.

357
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,160
If we

358
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:32,160
only performed in our county,

359
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,800
letting He Dachui play would be fine.

360
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,200
But don't forget,

361
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:38,600
we're going to the Beishan Showcase.

362
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:40,040
Experts in the whole region

363
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:42,160
and the whole province will be there.

364
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,280
And our kids

365
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:46,560
are just a bunch of rookies anyway.

366
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,720
Even Yi Qing'e

367
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:49,960
has been really inconsistent lately.

368
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:52,360
If the band drags them down,

369
00:22:52,360 --> 00:22:53,360
what to do?

370
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,160
Anyway,

371
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,800
this is your first show in charge.

372
00:23:04,280 --> 00:23:05,280
Let's sit down and talk.

373
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:07,680
Sit down first.

374
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:16,920
You think I don't want
Hu Sanyuan on drums?

375
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:19,360
I want him back in the troupe too.

376
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:21,160
But I can't decide.

377
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:24,280
You run the troupe

378
00:23:24,520 --> 00:23:26,200
but can't decide?

379
00:23:27,280 --> 00:23:29,120
Are you just a shrine idol?

380
00:23:29,560 --> 00:23:31,080
Only good for prayers and incense?

381
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,400
That's enough. Drop it.

382
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,440
Watch your mouth.

383
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,320
Loose talk brings trouble.

384
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,160
That's true anytime.

385
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:40,480
You forgot?

386
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:50,120
Yi Qing'e stars or Hu Sanyuan drums.

387
00:23:50,520 --> 00:23:51,840
You can only have one. Who?

388
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:53,880
Why only one?

389
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,960
Answer me first.

390
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,320
Yi Qing'e.

391
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:00,160
Then Hu has to step aside.

392
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:02,360
What kind of nonsense is that?

393
00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:04,640
Anyone but Yi Qing'e

394
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,360
can play Mu Guiying,

395
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:08,040
and Hu can still drum.

396
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,040
That's it.

397
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:11,200
What do you mean?

398
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:12,600
I don't get it.

399
00:24:13,360 --> 00:24:15,880
Yi Qing'e and Chu Jiahe are competing.

400
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:18,640
Yi Qing'e already has the upper hand.

401
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,320
Think about it.

402
00:24:21,320 --> 00:24:22,400
Now,

403
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:25,520
if her uncle, just freed, drums for her,

404
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:28,840
how can the kid perform later?

405
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:31,720
Now, even if I ask Hu Sanyuan to drum,

406
00:24:32,080 --> 00:24:33,080
he won't say yes.

407
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,520
Step back to move forward.

408
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:38,400
That's how we protect Yi Qing'e.

409
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:39,800
Her uncle

410
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:41,480
understands that.

411
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:36,900
(Boys' Dorm)

412
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:45,080
Master, your breathing sounds worse.

413
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:24,840
This juice boiled from elm bark

414
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:27,120
does wonders for the sideburns.

415
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:29,600
Flat and smooth.

416
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:31,320
Neat, sleek, and well-shaped.

417
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:34,760
It slims chubby faces, plumps thin ones.

418
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,400
Mr. Gou.

419
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:38,280
With the sideburns on,

420
00:28:38,280 --> 00:28:39,240
you'd look gorgeous.

421
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,440
Maybe back then.

422
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:44,320
Now, even if you stuck
an elm all over my face,

423
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:45,440
it won't help.

424
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:37,020
(Restaurant)

425
00:29:37,020 --> 00:29:40,260
(It is a glorious, great cause)

426
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,800
This is all I can afford.

427
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,520
Waiter.

428
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:53,120
Bring us your best bottle.

429
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:53,960
Coming right up.

430
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:55,080
I can't afford it.

431
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:56,760
Then why treat me?

432
00:30:05,760 --> 00:30:06,800
Come on, talk.

433
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:08,120
What's the matter?

434
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,320
Did you read the drum score?

435
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,160
I tore it up.

436
00:30:14,520 --> 00:30:16,000
Right, I was reckless.

437
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,680
I shouldn't have given it there.

438
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:20,840
You get it all wrong.

439
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:23,240
Try me anywhere you want.

440
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:25,160
It ends the same. I tear it up.

441
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,920
Don't you get it?

442
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:32,280
You listen, Hu Sanyuan.

443
00:30:32,280 --> 00:30:33,680
Nail's life

444
00:30:34,120 --> 00:30:36,440
and your years of suffering in prison.

445
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,200
Wasn't that enough

446
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,760
for you to drop the bad habit?

447
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,280
Can't you just change?

448
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:42,120
You listen,

449
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:44,840
you're not the old Hu Sanyuan,

450
00:30:44,840 --> 00:30:46,880
and I'm not the old He Dachui either.

451
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,560
Act tough with others if you want,

452
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:50,400
but not with me.

453
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,920
I'm already being polite.

454
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:00,360
You're still the same He Dachui.

455
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,280
Not one bit has changed.

456
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:03,120
Come on.

457
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:04,200
How is that?

458
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,680
Know why you can never beat me?

459
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,720
Why?

460
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,920
You take me too seriously.

461
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,320
Who takes you seriously?

462
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:19,040
Can you be

463
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:21,400
more like Hu Sanyuan than me?

464
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:24,040
How could you possibly beat me?

465
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:30,840
Your technique isn't bad at all.

466
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:33,640
You're just focusing on the wrong thing.

467
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,600
Keep an open mind.

468
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,560
Think long-term.

469
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:39,520
Now that I've quit playing,

470
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:42,440
in our county and the Beishan Region,

471
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:44,240
who can outplay you?

472
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:46,720
- You're right.
- If you get stuck,

473
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:47,960
just ask me.

474
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:49,960
Why would I ask you?

475
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:51,600
I'll tell you.

476
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:52,920
I'm not playing anymore.

477
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,840
What are you afraid of?

478
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,000
Listen to you.

479
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:56,600
You still sound better than me.

480
00:31:57,120 --> 00:31:58,400
You're lecturing me?

481
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:00,440
Come on, cheers.

482
00:32:01,080 --> 00:32:02,600
Think long-term.

483
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,000
Mother, if you don't lose...

484
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,840
Stop.

485
00:32:36,240 --> 00:32:37,840
That's not on me, right?

486
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,680
I was following your

487
00:32:39,680 --> 00:32:41,120
nose-wiping tissue beat.

488
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:45,040
Are we rehearsing?

489
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,200
Can we still rehearse?

490
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:54,940
(Script)

491
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:17,880
What to do?

492
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,520
Say something.

493
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,920
We've run this scene for days.

494
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:25,120
The kid's getting worse.

495
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,720
We're running out of time.

496
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:28,720
We can't stay stuck here.

497
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:36,840
I want Chu Jiahe as Mu Guiying.

498
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,800
No way.

499
00:33:37,800 --> 00:33:38,720
Why not?

500
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:40,760
Chu Jiahe isn't Mu Guiying.

501
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:43,120
With Yi Qing'e's current state,

502
00:33:43,120 --> 00:33:44,520
she's even less like Mu Guiying!

503
00:33:44,520 --> 00:33:46,600
You don't know Dan, so keep quiet.

504
00:33:48,560 --> 00:33:49,920
Fine, you know Dan.

505
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:51,760
Then get her into the zone!

506
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:54,200
We can't have the whole crew run it

507
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,520
with her over and over again!

508
00:33:56,050 --> 00:33:56,920
If this keeps up,

509
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,840
everyone will be exhausted and lose

510
00:33:58,840 --> 00:33:59,720
their momentum!

511
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:01,520
Everyone has off days.

512
00:34:02,320 --> 00:34:04,320
I was in a worse state back then.

513
00:34:05,800 --> 00:34:07,640
Few are as carefree as you,

514
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:09,160
always so pumped up,

515
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:10,640
forgetting everything else on stage.

516
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,520
Don't get sidetracked.

517
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,640
Focus!

518
00:34:13,640 --> 00:34:14,760
What to do now?

519
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:16,880
Go straight to dress rehearsal.

520
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,680
Strapped on

521
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:21,200
the opera armor, she'll have no choice.

522
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,880
Look at him!

523
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:25,800
Never seen someone so fiercely protective!

524
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:01,560
Okay, good.

525
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:10,400
Holding someone in your heart...

526
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:12,640
That feeling...

527
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:14,720
I know it well.

528
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:20,120
My first time in the opera armor,

529
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,360
I was about your age.

530
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:25,320
When I was ten,

531
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,960
my family was too poor to feed me.

532
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,840
They sent me to the opera troupe.

533
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:32,080
I was short and frail.

534
00:35:32,080 --> 00:35:33,440
Master had me learn the Dan role.

535
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,000
When I was about your age,

536
00:35:37,560 --> 00:35:38,880
I also had someone in my heart.

537
00:35:40,160 --> 00:35:41,360
Whether eating or sleeping,

538
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,080
she was all I could

539
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:44,160
think about.

540
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:47,320
For a long while,

541
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:49,800
I couldn't sing a scene right.

542
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:53,440
Even Master's harsh blows did nothing.

543
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:09,800
That day,

544
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:13,640
Master put me in the opera armor too.

545
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:17,120
Once I wore that costume

546
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:18,520
and stood near the stage,

547
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:20,880
I suddenly felt

548
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:23,560
like I could command the world.

549
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,960
What I carried inside

550
00:36:29,600 --> 00:36:30,680
wasn't just one person.

551
00:36:32,720 --> 00:36:34,520
It held a whole army.

552
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:51,800
Remember,

553
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:54,120
you're not Yi Qing'e.

554
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,320
You are Mu Guiying.

555
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:22,640
Today's meeting

556
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,800
is a pre-battle rally.

557
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:27,160
After this,

558
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:31,040
our whole troupe is going to Beishan

559
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:33,800
for the regional arts showcase.

560
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:36,200
They call it an arts showcase,

561
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:38,800
but really, across the whole region,

562
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:40,240
eleven troupes will

563
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,680
compete in Qinqiang opera.

564
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,160
The County Party Committee and Government

565
00:37:44,720 --> 00:37:46,040
are taking this showcase

566
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,240
very seriously.

567
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:50,000
They even got us

568
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,680
a big coach just for the trip.

569
00:37:52,040 --> 00:37:53,280
We no longer have to

570
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:55,120
choke on wind and dust

571
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,800
on the way to our shows.

572
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,360
Our troupe was built

573
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:14,080
on the old opera company

574
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:15,680
thirty years ago.

575
00:38:16,200 --> 00:38:19,520
We once had countless glory days.

576
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:22,000
But for all kinds of reasons,

577
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,840
we once reached a point with no shows.

578
00:38:25,680 --> 00:38:27,000
But today,

579
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:28,920
under the Party's leadership,

580
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:31,440
and with our veteran artists' efforts,

581
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:34,840
our whole troupe has united,

582
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,960
and we're about to leave winter behind

583
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:39,840
and welcome a new spring!

584
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:07,200
Liu Ke.

585
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,480
She called you.

586
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,040
Let's switch seats.

587
00:39:13,960 --> 00:39:14,800
Why?

588
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:15,920
Just switch.

589
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,120
Why asking?

590
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:18,360
Just do it. Get up.

591
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,440
Please, sit.

592
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,360
Play well.

593
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,240
Why looking at me?

594
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:35,800
Keep playing.

595
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:09,760
Master Gou.

596
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,120
Master Gou.

597
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:13,640
Look behind you.

598
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:36,680
♪Winnow, winnow, winnowing buckwheat♪

599
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:42,720
♪Winnow, winnow, one, two, hey♪

600
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:46,440
♪A girl's winnowing buckwheat by the door♪

601
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:50,440
♪Down the road comes a silly fellow♪

602
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:54,560
♪He says, "Young girl, go slow"♪

603
00:40:54,560 --> 00:40:58,800
♪"Let me pass by your front door"♪

604
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:02,680
♪Winnow, winnow, one, two, hey♪

605
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:06,560
♪A girl's winnowing buckwheat by the door♪

606
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:10,160
♪Down the road comes a silly fellow♪

607
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:14,280
♪He says, "Young girl, go slow"♪

608
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:19,160
♪"Let me pass by your front door"♪

609
00:41:20,240 --> 00:41:24,320
♪He says, "Young girl, go slow"♪

610
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:29,800
♪"Let me pass by your front door"♪

611
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:31,960
♪Hey-yo, hey-yo♪

612
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:37,240
♪Hey now, hey now, yo♪

613
00:41:59,010 --> 00:41:59,960
Sanyuan.

614
00:42:00,420 --> 00:42:02,820
I hear the County Troupe's going to Beishan.

615
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:04,290
Your niece will be onstage.

616
00:42:04,340 --> 00:42:05,340
Why not go to watch?

617
00:42:05,620 --> 00:42:06,560
I'll go.

618
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:07,680
Then

619
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:09,600
why hang around with me?

620
00:42:09,600 --> 00:42:10,490
I'll go tomorrow.

621
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,290
Move aside.

622
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:24,480
That's the troupe's van.

623
00:42:27,690 --> 00:42:28,960
- Master Song!
- Pull over!

624
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:30,320
Pull over!

625
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,480
Sanyuan? What are you here?

626
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,440
That's Hu Sanyuan.

627
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,320
How's it going?

628
00:42:33,370 --> 00:42:34,340
Heading to Beishan for the show?

629
00:42:34,370 --> 00:42:35,280
Yeah.

630
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:36,600
Can I come with you?

631
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:37,440
Sure. Hop in.

632
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,480
- Come here.
- Hop in.

633
00:42:38,520 --> 00:42:39,560
Here, here.

634
00:42:40,050 --> 00:42:40,960
I'm getting in.

635
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:41,880
Get in from the back.

636
00:42:41,880 --> 00:42:42,800
- Okay, okay.
- Careful.

637
00:42:43,640 --> 00:42:45,440
- Help me up.
- Master Hu, why here?

638
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:47,530
- Make room.
- Come on.

639
00:42:47,530 --> 00:42:48,370
Sit, sit.

640
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:49,520
Let's go.

641
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,400
I was thinking,

642
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:51,480
it's Qing'e's performance,

643
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,720
how could you miss it?

644
00:42:52,720 --> 00:42:53,800
Of course, I'll be there.

645
00:42:54,490 --> 00:42:55,440
Sanyuan!

646
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,520
Get me a ticket!

647
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:57,840
I'll come find you then.

648
00:42:58,640 --> 00:43:00,120
Here, take this straw hat.

649
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:06,940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

650
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:11,210
My last show was right here.

651
00:43:11,760 --> 00:43:13,080
My consecutive fire-breathing

652
00:43:13,280 --> 00:43:14,360
went badly.

653
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:15,600
Harder!

654
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:16,680
You're always

655
00:43:16,980 --> 00:43:18,480
the best Dan actor.

656
00:43:25,110 --> 00:43:26,880
Too weak. Stronger, stronger.

657
00:43:26,880 --> 00:43:27,760
Why don't you do it?

658
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:28,680
Move, move.

659
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:29,920
Listen to me.

660
00:43:29,920 --> 00:43:31,920
For fire breathing, just take it easy.

661
00:43:31,920 --> 00:43:32,830
Don't push yourself.

662
00:43:33,090 --> 00:43:34,080
Remember that.

663
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:41,620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

664
00:43:43,090 --> 00:43:47,930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

665
00:43:49,370 --> 00:43:53,560
♪We met and brushed past♪

666
00:43:55,120 --> 00:44:02,420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

667
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:20,540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

668
00:44:22,140 --> 00:44:27,710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

669
00:44:28,830 --> 00:44:32,890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

670
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:39,610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

671
00:44:40,770 --> 00:44:44,970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

672
00:44:46,010 --> 00:44:51,640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

673
00:44:52,810 --> 00:44:57,500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

674
00:44:58,180 --> 00:45:03,350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

675
00:45:04,020 --> 00:45:09,050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

676
00:45:10,080 --> 00:45:15,510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

677
00:45:15,890 --> 00:45:21,170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

678
00:45:22,120 --> 00:45:27,930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

679
00:45:27,930 --> 00:45:33,350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

680
00:45:33,900 --> 00:45:39,410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

681
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:44,920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

682
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:51,220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

683
00:45:52,020 --> 00:46:01,050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪

